info.author: Mike 'Fuzzy' Partin
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
oStri is an object subclassing str, and providing Cython optimized match() and
sub() methods, wrapping the standard C library (POSIX).

Requirements:
gcc or other C compiler, POSIX compatible libc, Python (tested with 2.6.X),
Cython (to regenerate C bindings)
info.name: ostri
info.summary: A string-like object with Cython optimized match() and sub() methods.
